data.description: This beautiful, classic brick ranch features 3 bed 2 baths, a covered front porch, oversized 2 car carport with storage, hardwood floors, beautiful kitchen with a bar area and view to the dining room, separate laundry room, sun room, large deck with above ground pool and hot tub, tv and entertaining area perfect for get togethers and no HOA.  This charming home has so much to offer at a great price and is move in ready.
